## Proposed changes

follow up #37090

support reuse sql cache when use variable as partition predicate and variable change:
```sql
set @dt='2024-07-16';
-- create cache 1
select * from tbl where dt = @dt;

set @dt='2024-07-17';
-- create cache 2, will not invalidate cache 1
select * from tbl where dt = @dt;

set @dt='2024-07-16';
-- reuse cache 1
select * from tbl where dt = @dt;
```
